Package unificationProblem

Class InputParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • unificationProblem.InputParser
  • public class InputParser
extends java.lang.Object
    The class InputParser handles the input. [a - t] are function symbols and u is the fist variable. This means that constants are function symbols with arity zero and [u - z] are variables. Names are witten in UPPER case letters.
    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Jan-Michael Holzinger & Sophie Hofmanninger
